    public abstract static class JuxtaProfiler.InitTimedCleanup
extends Object
implements JuxtaProfiler.ITimed
    Default implementation of JuxtaProfiler.ITimed which includes an untimed `init()` and `cleanup()` phase wrapped around the actually profiled `timed()` method.
